azoe, N., (1995) J. Mater. Chem., 5, p. 1391; Imanaka, N., Murata, T., Adachi, G., (1993) Denki Kagaku (Presently, Electrochemistry), 61, p. 909; Imanaka, N., Hirota, Y., Adachi, G., (1995) Sens. Actuators, B, 24-25, p. 380; Imanaka, N., Okazaki, Y., Adachi, G., Chem. Lett., 1999, p. 939; Imanaka, N., Okazaki, Y., Adachi, G., J. Mater. Chem., in Press; noteYamamoto, T., (1999), M. D. Thesis, Osaka University, Osaka, Japan","Adachi, G.-Y.; Department of Applied Chemistry, Faculty of Engineering, Osaka University, 2-1 Yamadaoka, Suita, Osaka 565-0871, Japan",,,,,,,,03667022,,,,"English","Chem. Lett.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-0034339648
